{
  "stem": "24111.2",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Or another one was taking the opportunity and went to the United-- had the opportunity to go to the United States.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "That was-- I am-- I'm talking about the time just before the-- the war in Poland, 1939.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So slowly, part of my family disappeared.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "In matter of fact, more than half of the original 200,000 managed to leave Austria before September of 1938.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Most of my family left.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] I know that records were kept.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And of course, suddenly you saw an emptiness around you.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Faces you knew were gone.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And when you asked what happened with so-and-so, oh, he got the affidavit or he got on a children's-- he got on a children's transport to England or to Sweden.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Some of those people unfortunately left and were caught a second time, because they left and went to Hungary, or they left and went to Czechoslovakia, or left and went to Yugoslavia.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Some of them had relatives, which made it possible to them.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So a large portion of people left.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I had also a cousin working in the [NON-ENGLISH] in Vienna.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And he worked in a particular department of the [NON-ENGLISH], which had all the records of the Jewish people of Vienna.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "His name was Ernst Weiss.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And me having nowhere to go, I lived with his father and mother in his-- in their apartment.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And one day he came to me and he said, Bob, the Germans requested lists from us.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I think it would be a good idea if you would go and voluntarily [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] say you want to go into the Arbeitsdienst, which is called workers-- that you want to work for them.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "For the Germans.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I did this.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
